<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1289] Remove &quot;hbase.fully.distributed&quot; option and update docs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1289</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &quot;hbase.fully.distributed&quot; boolean property is excessive. We should replace it by using &quot;local&quot; in &quot;hbase.master.hostname&quot; as we were doing before with &quot;hbase.master&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12419404">HBASE-1289</key>
            <summary>Remove &quot;hbase.fully.distributed&quot; option and update docs</summary>
